          -->{{nowrap|1=<!--
              -->{{#iferror:<!--
                -->{{#ifexpr:{{{HDI}}}>1 <!--
                 -->| {{error|Error: HDI value greater than 1}}<!--Handled by outer #iferror, not visible to users--><!--
